== COI violation ==

Hi, I've reverted all of your edits across the pages you've worked on, under our [[VRCWiki:Conflicts_of_interest]] policy. The policy says you should not directly create/edit content you are personally or professionally involved with, since it's hard to stay neutral about a subject you're close to.

This isn't a judgment of your intentions, and you're still welcome to contribute.

When you have a moment, it's worth reading through [[VRCWiki:How_to_Contribute]] and the [[VRCWiki:Contributor_hub]], along with our other policies and guidelines, so you know what to expect going forward. If you'd prefer to talk it through, you're welcome to join the wiki Discord at https://wiki.vrchat.com/discord, where editors are happy to help and answer questions.

Let me know if you have any questions about how this works. [[User:Usr 2c0d9735-9342-4db3-9c48-5eb152581b08|Tony_Lewis]] ([[User talk:Usr 2c0d9735-9342-4db3-9c48-5eb152581b08|talk]]) 01:07, 9 June 2026 (UTC)